I am pretty low too (g5 solo and flex, p5 3v3) but I think what helped me was consistently warding harald/baron/dragon. Even if your team is not in a position to contest it, knowing the enemy team is busy will let you take an objective on the other side of the map more quickly and confidently.
{{sticker:vlad-salute}}

Edit: also if you are a jungle ping before coming in to gank because teammates never seem to notice you otherwise for some reason.
